{"tid":2395523,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Dukascopy 報稅問題","createTime":"2021-02-05T03:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T14:45:18.000Z","uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"af26d4e661be6f22c6c9498b555442c8f949968f","tid":2395523,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"Your account will be reported to Swiss tax authority for Automatic Exchange of Information (&quot;AEOI&quot;) &ndash; please check tax residence<br />\n<br />\nDear Sir, Dear Madam,<br />\n<br />\nYou receive this message because Dukascopy Bank SA (&quot;Dukascopy&quot;) is preparing to communicate certain information related to your account and to you and/or to other holder(s) or beneficial owner(s) of your account to the Swiss Federal Tax Administration (&quot;FTA&quot;) by 30.06.2021 for the purpose of AEOI.<br />\nThe FTA will transfer the information received from Dukascopy to relevant tax authorities of the states having signed an agreement with Switzerland for AEOI (&quot;Partner States&quot;) in order to fight against tax evasion. <br />\n<br />\nAccording to our records, at least one holder or beneficial owner of your account had tax residence in a Partner State on 31.12.2020.<br />\n<br />\nPlease be so kind to verify and complete your tax information online.<br />\n<br />\nWe determined the tax residence of the persons/entities linked to your account based on their home/corporate address registered in our books or via the tax information you provided to us. <br />\n<br />\nIf you believe that we may have wrongly determined their tax residence, please update us (i) by accessing the Account section / personal information / tax information of your online reporting if your account is linked to only one natural person or (ii) by writing to legal@dukascopy.com in all other cases (MCA, joint accounts, legal entities, several beneficial owners, etc.).<br />\n<br />\nIf you are not the (unique) holder and beneficial owner of the account, please transmit this message to all account holders and beneficial owners of your account having tax residence in at least one Partner State.<br />\n<br />\n有無人都收到emai？"},{"pid":"78b9b65d21bd945aaaae04ebcf61abc12c4ea10b","tid":2395523,"uid":290838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:06:44.000Z","msg":"收到呀 但即係點要報稅？"},{"pid":"b532d3f92cfd844a6b4f6e18f6c3c7c58640a137","tid":2395523,"uid":162954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78b9b65d21bd945aaaae04ebcf61abc12c4ea10b","tid":2395523,"uid":290838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:06:44.000Z","msg":"收到呀 但即係點要報稅？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d9a414f69881c5c617ec4fa5d0fc73cb072f21","tid":2395523,"uid":290838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b532d3f92cfd844a6b4f6e18f6c3c7c58640a137","tid":2395523,"uid":162954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78b9b65d21bd945aaaae04ebcf61abc12c4ea10b","tid":2395523,"uid":290838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:06:44.000Z","msg":"收到呀 但即係點要報稅？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df37071b548892e69828f1a531f29bd5e3034a8c","tid":2395523,"uid":290838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b532d3f92cfd844a6b4f6e18f6c3c7c58640a137","tid":2395523,"uid":162954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78b9b65d21bd945aaaae04ebcf61abc12c4ea10b","tid":2395523,"uid":290838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:06:44.000Z","msg":"收到呀 但即係點要報稅？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"h